<div
  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
  xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
  class="portlet" id="portlet-info">

  <h2>Remote bug trackers</h2>

  <div class="portletBody portletContent">

    <img src="/@@/info" alt="" />
    Launchpad is designed to help track the status of a bug upstream and in
    lots of different bug trackers. This is a list of the bug trackers that
    are registered with Launchpad. You can link a Launchpad bug to any bug in
    one of these, and Launchpad will monitor the status on that bug and report
    changes to the subscribers of the Launchpad bug.

  </div>

</div>
